{"tid":1993041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國防部公佈年前不明飛行物體影片","createTime":"2020-04-28T13:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T13:57:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f353932cad38bd4e590987d5ab1e26861fcb6df","tid":1993041,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:22:39.000Z","msg":"美國國防部周一 (27/4) 公佈三段由美國海軍戰機師拍下，疑似目擊不明飛行物體 (Unidentified Flying Object, UFO) 的影片。該影片年前在網上流出，一直未被公開確認。<br />\n<br />\n該三段上載至國防部的影片中，其中一段於 2004 年 11 月 ，另外兩段則在及 2015 年 1 月拍攝。首段是由研究外星人組織 To The Stars Academy of Arts and Science 在 2007 年公佈，其餘兩段則在 2017 年由《紐約時報》發表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6rWOtrke0HY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6rWOtrke0HY&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=aa74d66e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6rWOtrke0HY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tf1uLwUTDA0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ftf1uLwUTDA0&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=42f11d00\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tf1uLwUTDA0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wxVRg7LLaQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwxVRg7LLaQA&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=6006adaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wxVRg7LLaQA</a><br />\n<br />\n國防部聲明指，海軍去年已確認三段流傳多年影片為戰機師所拍；在詳細審核後⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/cosmos/美國防部公佈年前不明飛行物體影片/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%89%A9%E9%AB%94%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=6af25362\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%89%A9%E9%AB%94%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%2F&h=5be447e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/cosmos/美國防部公佈年前不明飛行物體影片/</a>"},{"pid":"7d61fc7b0031345f5717d5c10d77012d54df87f2","tid":1993041,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}